{"tid":1930182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽到個故仔幾好笑,有狗仔手足老豆迫佢去英國讀書,佢唔肯只肯返中國讀話點解去做二等人","createTime":"2020-03-17T11:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T11:49:13.000Z","uid":179775,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6df9696a9fa5e4f4dab9967561ff9c03e8a642b4","tid":1930182,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老婆聽佢同事講<br />\n<br />\n黑警想個仔下年去英國讀書<br />\n知個仔黃既<br />\n咁個仔講明中國幾好幾好<br />\n唔想去害我祖國既國家<br />\n講一輪野佢老豆知咩事<br />\n只係放一句叫佢唔好拎自己前途鬥氣<br />\n個手足即時話你都知中國唔好既咩<br />\n但你又成日讚中國點叻點叻<br />\n我信老豆渣"},{"pid":"eb02a9e75e6a1edb45d295d2ded14c69bcbdccb6","tid":1930182,"uid":96182,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"班狗身體很誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71788be553088b0029a28436ede063b0876a199a","tid":1930182,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:32:16.000Z","msg":"根本全世界都知中國垃圾"},{"pid":"74f8b4946063fcdaef7e927d4a94469b67668d7d","tid":1930182,"uid":304856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"傳聞證供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班犬隻咪又係當香港人敵人，係到鬥氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日夜夜諗盡辦法點樣折磨/綁架香港人。佢地都知自己會變condom（中共點會俾呢班以下犯上嘅犬隻活得過反送中），但日日咪都係做政權打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee177036098fc43dbc215692b656af01b4682a80","tid":1930182,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"74f8b4946063fcdaef7e927d4a94469b67668d7d","tid":1930182,"uid":304856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"傳聞證供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo